        {
            "title": "西彎河夾公仔機店一連兩日遭淋油刑毀 警追緝3男女",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"蔡楚輝攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0532344f71b8d7ad35d220c2604d08cd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030106235035637.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">蔡楚輝攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西彎河夾公仔機店一連兩日遭淋油刑毀。今日清晨4時許，筲箕灣道57-87號太安樓商場地下一間夾公仔機店「狼之物」遭人淋紅油。昨日清晨，「狼之物」同位於太安樓商場內、相距約50米的另一間夾公仔機店也遭到相同手法破壞。\n\n</p>\n<p>現場消息指，案發時有兩男一女犯案，女的負責「睇水」，兩男手持鐵和一桶紅油進入店舖，先砸破店內多部機器，再向機器和店面潑紅油，然後逃去無蹤。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>警方接報到場後封鎖店舖調查，暫時未知該店遭破壞原因，不排除兩日事件為同一幫人所為。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055615/即時-港聞-西彎河夾公仔機店一連兩日遭淋油刑毀-警追緝3男女",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-01 06:31:42",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西區19歲醉娃疑失足墮海  熱心青年落水救人",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"網上圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1e2e2b21bf40a6ed7f4f0211df75622a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030106004533627.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">網上圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西區堅尼地城發生失足墮海事件，引發熱心市民落水救人。事發於昨日（28日）晚上7時許，卑路乍灣海濱長廊近臨時巴士總站位置，一名19歲女子懷疑因醉酒失足墮海，保安見狀馬上報警。\n\n</p>\n<p>情急期間，一名22歲姓江青年見義勇為，跳下海中欲救人，最終兩人由趕至的消防救起，清醒送瑪麗醫院治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111074/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"水警船將少女和青年救起。網上影片截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/899e8e86a58638610727d9b95b340cff/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-02-28_at_9_39_24_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        水警船將少女和青年救起。網上影片截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111075/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"水警船載送少女及青年往醫院治理。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c2b65a52aad8344c62ae99d8f2a3c36b/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-02-28_at_9_41_55_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        水警船載送少女及青年往醫院治理。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111076/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防派員到場拯救。網上圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03433d150ba200644bebda8f64c74bc9/2025-03/Screenshot_2025-02-28_at_9_42_22_PM.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防派員到場拯救。網上圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
